%F A396612 Equals (sqrt(3)/4 - (11*sqrt(5) + 25)*Pi/600 + (5/4 + 3/sqrt(5))*arcsinh(3/2 - sqrt(5)/2))/(2*(5 + sqrt(5)))^(1/3) (Dominik Beck, personal communication).
